    <item>
      <title>中国地方债务市场违约金额创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/record-defaults-hit-800-billion-chinese-municipal-debt-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国地方债务市场不透明角落的违约率飙升至历史新高，令那些以为这些证券有国家隐性担保的投资者陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/record-defaults-hit-800-billion-chinese-municipal-debt-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
